These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: sports, disaster, musical, family
Nationality: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
2. Movie-Genre:sports == Nationality:turkish##1
3. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
4. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Movie-Genre:family is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | family | musical | disaster | sports   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Movie-Genre: comedy, thriller, family, action
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. Movie-Genre:action == Sport:soccer##1
2. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the far right##1
3. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the right of Movie-Genre:action##1
4. Movie-Genre:action is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | family | action | thriller | comedy    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

