.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Music-Genre: dubstep, disco, funk, classical
Movie-Genre: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
2. Music-Genre:dubstep == Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Music-Genre:classical##1
5. Music-Genre:funk is on the left of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep | classical | funk   | disco |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

