2. Transport:car is on the left of Cigar:vegafina##1
3. Cigar:aristoff is on the left of Cigar:bongani##1
4. Cigar:vegafina == Transport:snowmobile##1
5. Transport:boat is on the left of Cigar:siglo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | bongani | siglo | vegafina   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 